el="nofollow">TikTok Shop</a> and How Do I Access It?`,answer:`<div>
            <b>TikTok Shop</b> is an integrated e-commerce platform within the
            <a href="${(0,_.YaX)({host:o,region:t||""})}" rel="nofollow">
              TikTok app
            </a>
            , allowing users to discover and purchase products directly from videos, live streams, and creator
            profiles.
          </div>
          <div>
            <b>How to Access</b>:
            <ul>
              <li>
                <b>In-App</b>: Open TikTok and tap the <b>"Shop"</b> tab or the shopping bag icon.
              </li>
              <li>
                <b>Through Videos</b>: Click on product links showcased in videos.
              </li>
              <li>
                <b>Profile Storefronts</b>: Visit a seller's profile and tap on their
                <b>"Shopping"</b> tab.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>`,keywords:["TikTok Shop","TikTok Shop App","TikTok Shop Login","How to Look Through TikTok Shops"]},{question:"How Do I Get TikTok Shop Promo Codes and Free Shipping?",answer:`<div>
          To obtain <b>TikTok Shop promo codes</b> and <b>free shipping codes</b>:
          <ul>
            <li>
              <b>
                Follow <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@tiktokshop_us" rel="nofollow">Official Accounts</a>
              </b>
              : Keep an eye on TikTok Shop's official promotions.
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Engage with Creators:</b> Influencers may share exclusive <b>promo codes</b> during live
              streams.
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>First Order Discounts:</b> New users often receive a <b>promo code for the first order</b>.
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Seasonal Sales:</b> Look out for discounts during holidays.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>`,keywords:["TikTok Shop Promo Code","TikTok Shop Free Shipping Code","TikTok Shop Promo Code First Order","TikTok Shop Gift Card"]},{question:"Is TikTok Shop Safe and Legitimate to Buy From?",answer:`<div>
            Yes, <b>TikTok Shop is safe and legitimate</b>. It provides
            <a href="https://seller-us.tiktok.com/university/essay?knowledge_id=4186564050224897" rel="nofollow">
              secure payment options
            </a>
            and verifies sellers to protect buyers.
          </div>
          <div>
            <b>Tips for Safety:</b>
            <ul>
              <li>Purchase from verified sellers with positive reviews.</li>
              <li>Read product descriptions carefully.</li>
              <li>Use secure payment methods within the app.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>`,keywords:["Is TikTok Shop Safe","Is TikTok Shop Legit","Can You Trust TikTok Shop"]},{question:"How Do I Sell on TikTok Shop?",answer:`<div>
          To start selling on TikTok Shop:
          <ol>
            <li>
              <b>Register as a Seller:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Visit the
                  <b>
                    <a href="https://seller.tiktok.com" rel="nofollow">TikTok Shop Seller Center</a>
                  </b>
                  .
                </li>
                <li>Sign up using your TikTok account or email.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Provide Business Information:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>Submit necessary documents for verification.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>List Your Products:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>Add product details and images.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Promote Your Products:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Use videos, live streams, and the
                  <b>
                    <a href="https://getstarted.tiktok.com/affiliates" rel="nofollow">TikTok Shop Affiliate Program</a>
                  </b>
                  .
                </li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>`,keywords:["How to Sell on TikTok Shop","TikTok Shop Seller","TikTok Shop Creator"]},{question:"Can I Sell Digital Products on TikTok Shop?",answer:`<div>
          Currently, <b>TikTok Shop primarily supports physical products</b>. To sell digital products:
          <ul>
            <li>
              <b>Check Policies:</b> Review the latest
              <a href="https://seller-ph.tiktok.com/university/essay?knowledge_id=7654193087743745" rel="nofollow">
                guidelines in the Seller Center
              </a>
              .
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Compliance:</b> Ensure digital products meet TikTok's standards.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>`,keywords:["Can You Sell Digital Products on TikTok Shop","TikTok Shop Policies"]},{question:"How Do I Add a TikTok Shop Link to My Video?",answer:`<div>
          To add a shop link to your TikTok video:
          <ul>
            <li>
              <b>Create Your Video:</b> Record and edit as usual.
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Add Link Before Posting:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Tap on <b>"Add Link"</b>.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Select <b>"Product"</b>.
                </li>
                <li>Choose the item from your TikTok Shop listings.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Post Your Video:</b> The product link will appear on your video.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>`,keywords:["How to Add TikTok Shop Link to Video","TikTok Shop Integration"]},{question:"How Do I Connect Shopify to TikTok Shop?",answer:`<div>
          To connect your Shopify store:
          <ol>
            <li>
              <b>Install TikTok App on Shopify:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>Go to Shopify App Store.</li>
                <li>
                  Install the <b>TikTok channel</b> app.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Link Accounts:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>Follow prompts to connect TikTok and Shopify.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Sync Products:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>Select products to feature on TikTok Shop.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Set Up Tracking:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>Install TikTok Pixel for analytics.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>`,keywords:["How to Connect Shopify to TikTok Shop","Shopify TikTok Shop Integration"]},{question:`How Long Does TikTok Shop Take to Deliver and Can I
          <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/discover/how-to-track-orders-on-tiktok" rel="nofollow">Track My Order</a>?`,answer:`<div>
          Delivery times vary depending on the seller and shipping method.
          <ul>
            <li>
              <b>Estimated Delivery:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>Provided at checkout or in order details.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Order Tracking:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Go to <b>"Orders"</b> in TikTok Shop.
                </li>
                <li>Select your order to view tracking information.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>`,keywords:["How Long Does TikTok Shop Take to Deliver","TikTok Shop Order Tracking"]},{question:"Why Is TikTok Shop So Affordable?",answer:`<div>
          TikTok Shop often offers lower prices due to:
          <ul>
            <li>
              <b>Direct Sales Model:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>Sellers can reduce costs by selling directly to consumers.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <b>Promotions and Discounts:</b>
              <ul>
                <li>Frequent sales events and promo codes.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <li>
            <b>High Competition:</b>
            <ul>
              <li>Sellers compete on price to attract buyers.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </div>`,keywords:["Why Is TikTok Shop So Cheap","TikTok Shop Deals"]},{question:`What Is the TikTok Shop
          <a href="https://seller-us.tiktok.com/university/essay?knowledge_id=3253210454181634" rel="nofollow">
            Return Policy
          </a>
          and How Do I Cancel an Order?`,answer:`<ul>
          <li>
            <b>Return Policy:</b>
            <ul>
              <li>Varies by seller, but generally allows returns within 14-30 days.</li>
              <li> Items must be unused and in original packaging.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <b>How to Return:</b>
            <ul>
              <li>
                Go to <b>"Orders"</b>.
              </li>
              <li>Select the item and initiate a return.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <b>Canceling an Order:</b>
            <ul>
              <li>If the order hasn't shipped, you can cancel it from the order details page.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>`,keywords:["TikTok Shop Return Policy","How to Cancel TikTok Shop Order","TikTok Shop Refunds"]}];return(0,i.jsx)(h,{items:r})},y={container:"container-gZCf_v",content:"content-Rkvsb7"},v=e=>{let{details:t=[],isBot:o}=e,[r,s]=(0,a.useState)(!!o);return(0,i.jsxs)("div",{className:y.container,children:[(0,i.jsx)("div",{className:y.title+(r?" text-color-UIText1Display":" text-color-UIText3")+" P1-Semibold  cursor-pointer",onClick:()=>{s(!r)},children:"Discover"}),r&&(0,i.jsx)("div",{className:y.content+" overflow-y-auto",children:t.filter(e=>{let{name:t,url:o}=e;return!!t&&!!o}).map(e=>(0,i.jsx)("a",{href:e.url,className:"P3-Semibold text-color-UIText3 cursor-pointer no-underline hover:underline",children:e.name},e.name))})]})};var x=o(6986);let w="LeftPanel",T=e=>{let{title:t="",subModules:o,currentExpandedId:r,onExpand:s,isBot:l,pageName:n,firstEntrance:c}=e,[u,p]=(0,a.useState)(!!l);return(0,a.useEffect)(()=>{l||r===t||p(!1)},[r,l,t]),(0,i.jsxs)("div",{children:[(0,i.jsx)("span",{className:k()("P1-Semibold  cursor-pointer",{"text-color-UIText1Display":u,"text-color-UIText3":!u}),onClick:()=>{p(!u),null==s||s(t),(0,_.vq8)({section:"left_panel_footer_title",jump_url:t})},children:t}),(null==o?void 0:o.length)&&u?(0,i.jsx)("div",{className:"flex flex-col gap-6 mt-6",children:o.map(e=>(0,i.jsx)("a",{rel:e.rel,className:"P3-Semibold text-color-UIText3 cursor-pointer no-underline hover:underline",href:e.href,onClick:t=>{t.preventDefault();var o=e.href||"";let r=(0,_.W8f)({url:o,source:n||"",enter_method:w});(0,_.vq8)({section:"left_panel_footer_item",jump_url:r}),setTimeout(()=>{window.open(r,"_blank")},250)},children:e.text},e.text))}):null]})},F=e=>{let{isBot:t,pageName:o,firstEntrance:r,region:s,host:l}=e,[n,c]=(0,a.useState)(""),u=(e=>{let{region:t,isBot:o,host:r}=e||{},{t:i}=(0,x.$)(),a=(0,_.BzF)(t),s=_.wyG[a??_.Xzq.US].sellerHref;return[{title:i("ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_buy"),subModules:[...a===_.Xzq.US?[{text:i("tts_shop_download_download_button2"),hre